 "title": "Parley for Brandis (Part 3)",
 "summary": "Deep within the Imperial flagship over Selene, Luke Skywalker, Ai'kani, Johanna, and Kyrin Sh'vani -- the winged Chyleni carrying the rescued Brandis on her back -- fight their way down through ventilation shafts and decks, using lightsabers and collapsing walls to cut off pursuing Stormtroopers. Ai'kani senses that Grand Admiral Danik is no longer alone, the falling lights and dropping temperatures heralding the arrival of the Sith. The Jedi push toward deck 70 and the observation area as the dark presence closes in around them.",
